com.codamotion.rtnet
Class RTNetClient

java.lang.Object
  com.codamotion.rtnet.RTNetClient
Direct Known Subclasses:
RTNetClientExtensionCX1, RTNetClientExtensionGS16AIO
public class RTNetClient
extends Object

Provides the main interface for interacting with Codamotion RTNet server. Connection to server is established using connect. Streaming of data from the server is done by creating a stream using createDataStream and requesting data packets to be sent. The method for triggering data packets depends upon the current acquisition mode - see startAcqContinuous, startAcqContinuousBuffered, doSingleShotAcq for more information.

doAutoDiscoverServer

public static InetSocketAddress[] doAutoDiscoverServer()
Search for Codamotion Realtime Network Server using UDP broadcast discovery protocol.
